                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-white/60">Starter</p>
                  <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline justify-center gap-2">
                    <span class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">RM 0</span>
                    <span class="text-lg text-white/60">/forever</span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/60">Create unlimited invoices • Watermark removed on Pro</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4">
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <div class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-500/10">
                      <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <p class="font-medium text-white">Conversational invoice creation</p>
                      <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-white/60">Chat to create invoices instantly</p>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <div class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-500/10">
                      <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <p class="font-medium text-white">Live PDF preview</p>
                      <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-white/60">See changes as you type</p>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                    <div class="mt-0.5 flex h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-500/10">
                      <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-gray-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <p class="font-medium text-white">RM & SST ready</p>
                      <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-white/60">Malaysian compliance built-in</p>
                    </div>
                  </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mt-8">
                  <Button className="h-12 w-full rounded-full bg-white text-base font-semibold text-black shadow-lg transition-all hover:bg-gray-200">Start Creating Free Invoices</Button>
                  <p class="mt-3 text-center text-xs text-white/60">No credit card required</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <section id="faq" class="relative border-y border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] py-20 sm:py-28">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">Frequently asked questions</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-white/60">Everything you need to know about Invoice Agent</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12 space-y-4">
            <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/5 to-transparent p-6 transition-all hover:border-white/20">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between text-lg font-semibold text-white">
                <span>Is it really conversational?</span>
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-4 text-white/60">Yes. Describe your invoice in natural language — items, quantities, terms — and watch the PDF update live.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/5 to-transparent p-6 transition-all hover:border-white/20">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between text-lg font-semibold text-white">
                <span>Do you support Malaysian SST?</span>
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-4 text-white/60">We support RM currency and SST calculation out-of-the-box, with compliant formats for Malaysian businesses.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/5 to-transparent p-6 transition-all hover:border-white/20">
              <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between text-lg font-semibold text-white">
                <span>Can I use templates?</span>
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" /></svg>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-4 text-white/60">Choose from 10+ professional templates across Modern, Elegant, Corporate, and Creative styles.</p>
            </details>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12 text-center">
            <Button className="h-12 rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-8 text-white backdrop-blur-sm transition-all hover:bg-white/20">Contact Support</Button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Final CTA -->
      <section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-gray-800/10 to-gray-700/10 p-12 text-center backdrop-blur-sm sm:p-16">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10">
              <div class="absolute left-1/4 top-0 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-white/20 blur-3xl"></div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-gray-600/20 blur-3xl"></div>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">Build invoices at the speed of chat</h2>
            <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg text-white/60">Join teams creating professional invoices in minutes — no learning curve, just natural conversation.</p>
            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row">
              <Button className="group h-14 rounded-full bg-white px-10 text-base font-semibold text-black shadow-xl transition-all hover:scale-105">
                Start Creating Free Invoices
                <svg class="ml-2 h-5 w-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" /></svg>
              </Button>
              <Button className="h-14 rounded-full border border-white/20 bg-white/10 px-10 text-base font-semibold text-white backdrop-blur-sm transition-all hover:bg-white/20">Schedule a Demo</Button>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-white/40">Free plan available • SST-ready • Professional templates</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
